      "type": "text",
      "body": "<p class=\"question\">\n</p>"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "body": "\n        Oblicz sumę wielomianów \\(W_1\\) i \\(W_2\\), gdzie\n        \\[\n        \\begin{align*}\n        W_1(x)&amp;=7x^4-2x^3+5x+2\\\\\n        W_2(x)&amp;=4x^3+4x^2-5x+3\n        \\end{align*}\n        \\]\n        <small>\n            W takich zadaniach, jak i właściwie we wszystkich innych, należy przedstawić w najprostszej postaci, więc w tej sytuacji - zredukować wyrazy podobne.\n        </small>\n"
    },
    {
      "type": "spoiler",
      "label": "rozwiązanie",
      "body": "\n\n<div class=\"switch_steps\">\n<div class=\"switch_step\">\n                Mamy obliczyć\n                \\[\n                W_1(x)+W_2(x)=\\underline{7x^4-2x^3+5x+2}+\\underline{4x^3+4x^2-5x+3}\n                \\]\n                <p>\n                    Zauważmy, że oba wielomiany są w postaci uproszczonej, a potęgi zapisane w kolejności malejących wykładników (tzn. od największego do najmniejszego). Przyjrzyjmy się wyrazom obu wielomianów w tej kolejności.\n                </p>\n<p>\n                    Potęga \\(x^4\\) pojawia się tylko w \\(W_1\\), więc nie ma tu nic do upraszczania. Możemy zacząć zapisywać sumę:\n                </p>\n<div style=\"min-height: 2em;\">\n<span style=\"float: right;\">\n                        \\(W_1(x)+W_2(x)=7x^4+\\dots\\)\n                    </span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"switch_line\">\n                    Potęga \\(x^3\\): \\(\\quad -2x^3+4x^3=\\)\n                    <div class=\"switch_value\">\n                        &gt;&gt; wybierz &gt;&gt;\n                    </div>\n<div class=\"switch_value\">\n                        \\(-6x^3\\)\n                    </div>\n<div class=\"switch_value\">\n                        \\(2x^3\\)\n                    </div>\n<div class=\"switch_value\">\n                        \\(-8x^3\\)\n                    </div>\n                    .\n                    <div class=\"switch_show_next ks_button\">\n                        zatwierdź\n                    </div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"switch_step hidden\">\n<div style=\"min-height: 2em;\">\n<span style=\"float: right;\">\n                        \\(W_1(x)+W_2(x)=7x^4+2x^3+\\dots\\)\n                    </span>\n</div>\n                Potęga \\(x^2\\) pojawia się tylko w \\(W_2\\), więc tu też nie ma nic do upraszczania.\n                <div style=\"min-height: 2em;\">\n<span style=\"float: right;\">\n                        \\(W_1(x)+W_2(x)=7x^4+2x^3+4x^2+\\dots\\)\n                    </span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"switch_line\">\n                    Potęga \\(x^1\\): \\(\\quad 5x-5x=\\)\n                    <div class=\"switch_value\">\n                        &gt;&gt; wybierz &gt;&gt;\n                    </div>\n<div class=\"switch_value\">\n                        \\(0\\)\n                    </div>\n<div class=\"switch_value\">\n                        \\(10x\\)\n                    </div>\n<div class=\"switch_value\">\n                        \\(-10x\\)\n                    </div>\n                    .\n                    <div class=\"switch_show_next ks_button\">\n                        zatwierdź\n                    </div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"switch_step hidden\">\n                Na razie nic nie dopisujemy.\n                <div class=\"switch_line\">\n                    Potęga \\(x^0\\), czyli wrazy wolne: \\(\\quad 2+3=\\)\n                    <div class=\"switch_value\">\n                        &gt;&gt; wybierz &gt;&gt;\n                    </div>\n<div class=\"switch_value\">\n                        \\(5\\)\n                    </div>\n<div class=\"switch_value\">\n                        \\(6\\)\n                    </div>\n                    .\n                    <div class=\"switch_show_next ks_button\">\n                        zatwierdź\n                    </div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"switch_step hidden\">\n                Ostatecznie więc\n                <div style=\"min-height: 2em;\">\n<span style=\"float: right;\">\n                        \\(W_1(x)+W_2(x)=7x^4+2x^3+4x^2+5\\)\n                    </span>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "body": "<p class=\"question\">\n</p>"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "body": "\n        Oblicz różnicę wielomianów \\(W_1\\) i \\(W_2\\), gdzie\n        \\[\n        \\begin{align*}\n        W_1(x)&amp;=7x^4-2x^3+5x+2\\\\\n        W_2(x)&amp;=4x^3+4x^2-5x+3\n        \\end{align*}\n        \\]\n    "
    },
    {
      "type": "spoiler",
      "label": "rozwiązanie",
      "body": "\n\n<div class=\"switch_steps\">\n<div class=\"switch_step\">\n                Mamy obliczyć\n                \\[\n                W_1(x)-W_2(x)=\\underline{7x^4-2x^3+5x+2}-(\\underline{4x^3+4x^2-5x+3})\n                \\]\n                <p>\n                    Zacznijmy od znaków wyrazów odejmowanego wielomianu\n                </p>\n                \\[\n                W_1(x)-W_2(x)=\\dots-(\\color{red}{+}4x^3\\color{red}{+}4x^2\\color{red}{-}5x\\color{red}{+}3)\n                \\]\n                <div class=\"switch_line\">\n                    Po opuszczeniu nawiasu przyjmą postać\n                    <div class=\"switch_value\">\n                        &gt;&gt; wybierz &gt;&gt;\n                    </div>\n<div class=\"switch_value\">\n                        \\(4x^3-4x^2+5x-3\\)\n                    </div>\n<div class=\"switch_value\">\n                        \\(-4x^3-4x^2+5x-3\\)\n                    </div>\n<div class=\"switch_value\">\n                        \\(-4x^3+4x^2-5x+3\\)\n                    </div>\n                    .\n                    <div class=\"switch_show_next ks_button\">\n                        zatwierdź\n                    </div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"switch_step hidden\">\n                Po opuszczeniu nawiasu dostajemy:\n                \\[\n                \\begin{align*}\n                W_1(x)-W_2(x)&amp;=\\underline{7x^4-2x^3+5x+2}-(\\color{red}{+}4x^3\\color{red}{+}4x^2\\color{red}{-}5x\\color{red}{+}3)\\\\\n                &amp;=7x^4-2x^3+5x+2\\color{red}{-}4x^3\\color{red}{-}4x^2\\color{red}{+}5x\\color{red}{-}3\n                \\end{align*}\n                \\]\n                <p>\n                    Potęga \\(x^4\\) pojawia się tylko w \\(W_1\\), więc nie ma tu nic do upraszczania. Zacznijmy zapisywać różnicę:\n                </p>\n<div style=\"min-height: 2em;\">\n<span style=\"float: right;\">\n                        \\(W_1(x)-W_2(x)=7x^4+\\dots\\)\n                    </span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"switch_line\">\n                    Potęga \\(x^3\\): \\(\\quad -2x^3-4x^3=\\)\n                    <div class=\"switch_value\">\n                        &gt;&gt; wybierz &gt;&gt;\n                    </div>\n<div class=\"switch_value\">\n                        \\(-6x^3\\)\n                    </div>\n<div class=\"switch_value\">\n                        \\(2x^3\\)\n                    </div>\n<div class=\"switch_value\">\n                        \\(-8x^3\\)\n                    </div>\n                    .\n                    <div class=\"switch_show_next ks_button\">\n                        zatwierdź\n                    </div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"switch_step hidden\">\n<div style=\"min-height: 2em;\">\n<span style=\"float: right;\">\n                        \\(W_1(x)-W_2(x)=7x^4-6x^3+\\dots\\)\n                    </span>\n</div>\n                Potęga \\(x^2\\) pojawia się tylko w \\(W_2\\), ale wyraz \\(4x^2\\) jest\n                <strong>\n                    odejmowany\n                </strong>\n                , więc uzyskujemy:\n                <div style=\"min-height: 2em;\">\n<span style=\"float: right;\">\n                        \\(W_1(x)-W_2(x)=7x^4-6x^3-4x^2+\\dots\\)\n                    </span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"switch_line\">\n                    Potęga \\(x^1\\): \\(\\quad 5x+5x=\\)\n                    <div class=\"switch_value\">\n                        &gt;&gt; wybierz &gt;&gt;\n                    </div>\n<div class=\"switch_value\">\n                        \\(0\\)\n                    </div>\n<div class=\"switch_value\">\n                        \\(10x\\)\n                    </div>\n<div class=\"switch_value\">\n                        \\(-10x\\)\n                    </div>\n                    .\n                    <div class=\"switch_show_next ks_button\">\n                        zatwierdź\n                    </div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"switch_step hidden\">\n<div style=\"min-height: 2em;\">\n<span style=\"float: right;\">\n                        \\(W_1(x)-W_2(x)=7x^4-6x^3-4x^2+10x+\\dots\\)\n                    </span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"switch_line\">\n                    Potęga \\(x^0\\), czyli wrazy wolne: \\(\\quad 2-3=\\)\n                    <div class=\"switch_value\">\n                        &gt;&gt; wybierz &gt;&gt;\n                    </div>\n<div class=\"switch_value\">\n                        \\(5\\)\n                    </div>\n<div class=\"switch_value\">\n                        \\(-1\\)\n                    </div>\n<div class=\"switch_value\">\n                        \\(6\\)\n                    </div>\n                    .\n                    <div class=\"switch_show_next ks_button\">\n                        zatwierdź\n                    </div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"switch_step hidden\">\n                Ostatecznie więc\n                <div style=\"min-height: 2em;\">\n<span style=\"float: right;\">\n                        \\(W_1(x)-W_2(x)=7x^4-6x^3-4x^2+10x-1\\)\n                    </span>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n"
    },
